title: Mistakes Were Made, LoL eSports Story v 0.15
description:
Mistakes Were Made, a League of Legends eSports story.
v 0.15

Start reading Mistakes Were Made while it's still in Alpha, and even provide feedback or comments or critiques to help improve it by the time it reaches Beta.

"The global economy continues to tank well into the year 2016 and everyone is suffering from massive underemployment and working too many hours for minimum wage. At the same time, the competitive gaming and eSports industry continues to rise."


Version/Build 0.15 includes Chapters 0-15, as well as optional story content in the Logbook, and a reference section named the Library Cultura.
